  "prompt": "If I delete my Tinder account and uninstall the app, does my profile still show to those I've matched with?",
  "response": "If you delete your Tinder account, your profile will be removed from the platform, and it will no longer be visible to anyone, including those you've matched with. Uninstalling the app without deleting your account will not affect your visibility; your profile will still be active until you choose to delete it. However, once you delete your account, all your matches and messages will also be deleted. Make sure to save any important information before you do so!",
